Q. Really?
ARIYA JUTANUGARN: I was really nervous when she play.  I know she can do it, but I was just rooting for her so much.
Q. She has been so close so many times.
ARIYA JUTANUGARN: Yeah.
Q. Is there something special about doing it in L.A, because you guys love coming here?
ARIYA JUTANUGARN: Yeah, we come here a lot.  We really love to come here.
Q. How about her game and how it suits this course.  You don't have to hit it long here, do you?
ARIYA JUTANUGARN: So that not good for me.
